{"text": "This game is absoulutely amazing. I really suggest getting it. First of all i would just like too say that this is game is one of a kind... I mean there are some other similar games but they  doesnt give the same good feeling when playing this. The game is relaxing and difficult , and even frustrating at some points. But the frustration is gone in an instant as you start a new game. Physics works great never had a problem at all. Now i see alot of people complaining that its imposible too use a keyboard. But i can tell you right now that it isnt at all. Its really down too personal preference. Thats what i like. That you can change up controls and try something new. The brilliant part of this game is the seed function. Put in a series of numbers or words and a new level generates. Amazing how i played this for hours on hours end never got bored. This game is art. This game will be praised by many. Good job devs.  I want too say thank you for this amazing game you have made. Its really something you just want too play after a stressing work day and just feel relaxed. Only thing is that this game doesnt have music. I was kinda dissapointed put youtube is your friend. Maybe put on some zen music  if you want too relax, or some Trap music if you want too do sick stunts. Its a really fun game that i will enjoy for months. maybe even years. i will never stop playing this game. Its my favourite game on steam.", "appid": "732430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198412576744", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514635200.0}
