{"text": "This is the ultimate rally experience! After the arcade \"American style\" Dirt series,fortunately Codemasters decided to go back to its roots. This game instantly reminds me of the McRae series! Nice graphics,astonishing sound effects,superb gameplay and physics make this game one of the best racing titles of all time. You get around 50 cars,almost 100 stages with different conditions(all terrain-weather combinations available) plus daily-weekly-monthly multyplayer challenges and more.   If you like rally and racing games,this is an absolute purchase. Not for the faint of hearted, arcaders! quitters,but exclusively for hardcore-true gamers. Thank you Codemasters. The game goes on sale pretty often,offering lots of  value for money. I had more than 250hrs of gameplay before i finally uninstalled(which i regret and re-install) and there are no known issues/bugs/glitches,it runs smooth even in medium specs PC.", "appid": "310560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039646933", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0}
