{"text": "Ok, first, for those who compares to TF2 : CUT THE CRAP. Seriously dudes, of course it's not the same game at all, this one is from 99. Do you even remember how video games were in 99 ? TFC was a â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ revolution still active today with 100+ servers. It deserves respect, at least. Then, we can talk about the â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ veterans of TFC who still play today, after like 10 years, grenade spamming... The type of guy who annoys you to death because he kills you EVERY TIME calling you noob. Well, i'm this guy, and yeah, totally : you're a giant noob and it's fun to piss you off. We don't really need new players and it's always funny to see your Ragequit. If you have the good attitude, asking how basically grenades works and stuff, people will help you indeed, but 99,9% of time, people thought they will rek everyone ingame with their awesome skills and get frustrated. That's life, get over it. Now, I understand that TF2 originally people will not love this game, but still : don't criticize such a piece of art.", "appid": "20", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981956341", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1320148800.0}
