{"text": "This is one of the greatest games I've ever played. If it were a movie To the Moon would be on par with Titanic if not better. Coming from someone who doesn't get emotionally affected easily, believe me when I say if you want a heartfelt and sentimental experience worth every penny, you will want to buy this game. It's on the Humble Indie Bundle X now but you should definitely pay the $10 to buy it on steam. There is a huge amount of detail put into this RPG style game so you can explore every nook and cranny of his life and how it is like. With an amazing storyline and touching soundtrack you will feel like you are the one getting his wish fulfilled. Seriously stop reading this and buy it right now and it'll be the best 10 bucks you ever spent. The question I hope you will be left with at the end is, what does it really mean to be living the dream?", "appid": "206440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010490799", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "129", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1389355200.0}
