{"text": "Great Game guys, and really hard! I'm starting it again for thr 5th 'cause my group didn't do it again! It seems easy at the beginning, and maybe you'll think you can handle it, but as time goes on, you will start to think you'll never get out of that alive! You have to manage your resources carefully, and they will never be enough anyway! And even when you think you have reached a good point and the situation seems a bit good, something unexpected could happens, like a particular aggresive \"visit\" by a group of hostile survoivors, or unfortunate and not wanted fight during a \"scanvege tour\", and the situation will be f.u.b.a.r.! Also a very good grapich, it gives you the right feeling, all ruined and gray, and the good sad music complete it perfectly! An overview of my last game: -Day 1: 3 survivors met randomly and decided to build a safe house in a ruined multi-story building; They started to clean it up from rubbles and making it a bit more comfortable, building a chair, 2 beds, a stove and a water collector; Also started to scavenge the neighborhood, finding a lot of good materials, food and meds; -Day 15: The group grew up to 4 elements only to return straight back to 3 after a freshly arrived girl was killed while scavenging in a close, still inabhited villa; the group were really upset by it, moreover, she was carrying a lot of good usefull stuffs and a precious crowbar and they were unable to recover the package due to heavy fights nearby. The group were also in short of food and meds, and one of 'em was deeply wounded during a night raid in our safe house. -Day 25: group grew up again to 4, and managed to survive day by day trading some stuffs with a wandering trader and, sadly, by stealing food and meds from a couple of old people. They were still in desperate need of materials to upgrade the safehouse with advanced stuctures, like a garden to cultivate vegetables and homemade tobacco, and a distillery; a better stove was also needed. Weather changed and it started to snow, getting colder and colder, but not enough materials to build a good warming heater stove; there were no more materials to scanvenge 'cause all the knew places were blocked by fights. After 5 days fighting, the villa and all the other places were again accessible, and one of the survoivor decide to go back there to recover the package and to avenge the killed girl; he goes there and slaughtered the 2 pepole isnide, bringing back a lot of usefull stuffs...but not everyone appreciated it: after a few days, 2 of 'em rna away from the safehouse, unable to bear the weight of the situation; the arrive of another girl brought some hope to the 2 wounded and ill remaining survoirs but, unfortunate, she was killed by a sniper 3 day after, while returing back with aids; There were not much more to do for the other 2, especially after hostile raiders noticed their weakness and started to attack avery night... This is the game guys, and this is the war. Higly raccomanded game guys if you like the genre! If you like it, please follow my upcoming serie about it and about other good games on youtube and facebook on the white raven channel! PS: ITA speech! ;)", "appid": "282070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025632506", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1416657600.0}
