{"text": "Well what can I say...  This is already one of my favorite Open World RPG's of these past years and this should go without saying. After waiting  around 3 years (sadly I was not there from the start) this game has lived up to all the hype that I and other people have  been giving it. Yeah yeah, it has its bugs and glitches but I never experienced something so game breaking that I got frustrated. I would recommend this game to anyone who is interested in Open World's, RPG's and Historically accurate games, there are so many things you can do that are interesting and riveting. Quests are full of characters with their own identities and jobs for you take on your own shoulders.", "appid": "379430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198113113524", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518955200.0}
