{"text": "Honestly, this extremely simple yet enormously adorable game gives me a thought about kinetic energy movments and basic human survival.  While ostensibly, Human Fall Flat is the game created for everyone from male to female, and young to old. However, in reality, it reveals the true face of individuals which is a complete massacre being repeated as a mere entertainment. Literally, when there are 4 players playing this game together, instead of looking towards the game's ultimate goal of escaping, each players look for an entertainment, which is to kill his or her friends.  They grab, push, pull and throw their friends to never-ending gravitational abyss and laugh at victims' scream.  I can only say this shows how cruel human can be.  Overall, this game is very fun for Psychopaths who love murdering their own friends. :) And therefore, I enjoyed playing this game very much.", "appid": "477160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198402087955", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540296000.0}
