uined the atmosphere. Thank all of the sh*tty youtubers who brought the wave of REEEE to this title. Go play the actual SCP: Containment Breach, You'll have a far better experience. The only thing fun about this game is TKing whiny brats who try to team with SCPs.", "appid": "700330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049046290", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603713600.0}
