{"text": "Absolute Trash Game, this game makes nothing better or different than a lot of other (and better) survival games. So, you may ask, why is it trash, looking at the positive reviews? - You CANNOT get your loot back after dying, corpses are disappearing soo fast, sometimes you cant even manage to loot your hunting prey fast enough - Reason No 1 should be already enough, but it makes it even worse, that you die a lot because of very stupid reasons, like ridicolously high falling damage, bugs (ofc), cheaters, KOS, etc... - you waste too much time getting set up, with very high risk of losing it all every day - you dont have infinite or big storage possibilities, which could actually be a good thing, but its soooo small, you cant even store all the basics you need in the game, HUGE TURNOFF AGAIN - all those reasons make this game a tooooo big waste of time, you waste time looting & loose it, because bugs or you cant store it, etc.... If devs finally listen to community this could be a REALLY GREAT game, probably one of the greatest survival games of all time, this game is essentially dayZ with much better graphics, engine, playability, its much more stable, looks sooo good & its soo much fun, theres a lot of great ideas in this game, etc etc... but as i said, devs arent listen rn. soo...  NO RECOMMENDATION FOR NOW.", "appid": "299740", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987286350", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575720000.0}
