{"text": "EARLY ACCESS REVIEW I feel so scammed. *DO NOT BUY THIS GAME* The game is broken. It does not work. Not only that, but the devs seem to be leaving it in a broken state. It has been many months with no fixes to the bugs that make the game UNPLAYABLE. You can't power your ship, your ore detector will stop working, the wolves do not move anymore. IT IS BAD. The worst part is that they don't seem to be fixing it. Normally developers would do a bug fix patch and have this worked out within a week or two, but it has been several months and NO FIX. SCAM ALERT! **** UPDATED REVIEW*** I wanted to come play Space Engineers again to see the progress the Devs have made on the game, and potentially update my negative review to a positive one.  Unfortunately the game will not even boot up.   Stuck on the loading screen for so long, I even allowed the game to try to load over night, and came back to see that it was still loading when I woke up.  What a disappointment!", "appid": "244850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143355773", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530532800.0}
