{"text": "Review Edit, \"I really hope the Overload team reconsider starting up the oceana server.\" This is an incredible game, graphically immersive and very challenging mission wise depending on what difficulty you choose i love the missions but i love MP more.  Like many games that have not long come out of early access it has its fair share of bugs which is understandable and they will be sorted in time. Where i am torn is the lack of server support in the Oceana region, so i am dependent on servers in the states which i do not mind. In saying that the best server for me \"Oregon\" is a good 100ms ping slower than a North American server that is much further away in another 6Dof game where i can actually compete on a more equal footing with my stateside friends. Overall I love the game period! Pros: Graphically Impressive! The campaign/missions are fantastic and the story line is rich. The Control and feel of the game is excellent. Note: The ability to choose a server would be a nice addition Cons: There is only 1   No Server support in the Oceana region for MP which makes for a dreadful experience in MP. Yes i have tried the whole VPN thing and it does not work for me. Us server support is abysmal with the best US server giving me pings in the 280+ range while i can get pings of 160ms+ from the North American server of another 6Dof game which confounds me. Of Special Note: I have gifted this game to 2 friends one in Germany and one in New Zealand and plan to gift it to another so it has my support and it is a fantastic game. Finally i can not recommend the Multiplayer aspect of this game for players based in the Oceana region because of the frustrating and very weak server support from the states when i get incredible server support in a similar game. ie approximates 280ms+ as opposed to 160ms+ < this being from a server that is much further.  This review is open to change should there be an improvement in server support. I have enabled comments ( your right of reply ) so please be civil and constructive.", "appid": "448850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198371987867", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539950400.0}
