{"text": "In-app purchases. I would be fine with that if they had stated it on the store page (though I may not have purchased the game, due to it). If a developer is going to hide the fact there are in-game purchases (even if just cosmetic) they I would not suggest the game. If the fix this on the store page (or remove such transactions from the game) I will take another look at this review (and have more play time by then). And as far as I can tell, there is no way to earn them in-game either. Update: Still no Microtransactions tag on the store page. No longer an issue of the developer forgetting to add it. They seem to be leaving it off intentionally. Very deceptive, imho. Won't be buying from them again.", "appid": "361420", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970110818", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594641600.0}
