{"text": "Un jeux qui a un gros potentiel, mais qui est ruiner par la communautÃ© de counter strike, la majoritÃ© des joueur que j'ai croiser (680 heures) sont pour la plupart des personnes qui se permette d'insulter a chaque match, active leur micro pour rien, spam le tchat, mette de la musique.  Mais se n'est pas tout l'anticheat de valve \"VAC\" est inutile et ne marche pas, car les personnes continues de les utilisÃ©s, j'ai l'impression que les signalement que moi et mes amis faisont sont inutiles (aucun suivi). *ajout* depuis que le jeu est devenu un free to play, il y a une recrtudÃ©cence de cheateur, mais aussi de la multiplication des cancers sur chaque mode proposer par le jeu Le nouveau mode jeu (br) est nul et mal fait comparer a warface ou a call of duty black ops 4 et PUBG *nouvelle ajout* les nouvelles map sont sympa pour conclure :  je ne recommande pas se jeu si c'est pour jouer seul, mais pour jouer avec des amis en compÃ©titif le jeu est intÃ©ressant car il faut avoir une sinergie dans l'Ã©quipe *ajout* Depuis qu'il est free to play c'est de pire en pire, passer CS en FTP a tuer le jeu et a retirer tous le fun dans les autres mode de jeu et en compÃ©titif aussi", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130469628", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528545600.0}
{"text": "There's not much more to say on top of the other negative reviews here. They wanted to be innovative and wound up taking far more away from us than they gave. Very disappointing. I may be spoiled by the Dark Souls games but this left so much to desire. The apparent lack of creativity is nuts. The scenery may vary slightly but it's the same game the entire way through. You fight essentially the same mobs with the exact same stuff. With these 'boss fights' that are gimmicky and mostly simple, the journey between the bosses are basically the same the whole way though as well. I never thought I'd just want to be finished with a From Software game. Mix this with (sometimes) the worst AI I've seen in a game comparable to Skyrim, lack of reward (for both exploring [see fist fulls of ash] and sense of accomplishment), and 100 hits chipping away with deaths to 1 mistake or a goofy hitbox. They just took so much away from what we're used to (including all these items and builds and weapons, and no the prosthetic doesn't count). This is not to say this is not a good game however.. I would like to reiterate that while it's a \"good\" game, I have been spoiled by their capabilities with the souls games. This feels like they took a step in the wrong direction. Most people would probably say this is excellent and should do so. If you're looking for something to shine among their other accomplishments, this is far from that. TL;DR Good game - It's very disappointing as a From Software title. Read other negative reviews for more examples.. no reason to essentially copy paste.", "appid": "814380", "steamid": "profiles/76561197979211207", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553688000.0}
