{"text": "Sadly I have to agree with all the bad reviews...as a new player i didn't experience the game before they patched it so my opinion isn't comparative with older version. It actually miss depth...after 1 hour of gameplay, i saw there was no challenge...it's very bad beacause the game concept is good. unique craft system where you have to learn how to craft...maybe before...now you have an easy crafting guide, and craft everything is very easy. No monsters to face, just the enviroment and of course sharks. It could be a real challenge but alas actually  isn't, cause weather doesn't impact on you and i saw no sharks...There's nothing that pushes you to go to another island, as all isles have the same resources, so, after you easily build your shelter and your farm, what will you do? Why leave? To explore? Why not. But there's not much to explore...and also you have to wander the sea to pop wrecks up before you can explore them...no challenge  guys, and challenge is all in a survaival game, isn't it? GRAPHIC is good but it's not the same you see in the shop pictures. Plus if you really want to enjoy it you must play on ultra and here it goes very laggy. Play on high and honestly it's not bad but not that good either. Plus you can't notice far objects like wrecks, you have to move close to them. ANIMATIONS. Sorry guys, i respect the work of everyone but comon you can and you must do better! when you chop down a tree you just see your arm moving, some splinters, chopping sound and then the tree goes down. Why don't you try the forest and see the difference? I must say that I appreciate that you have to chop the tree in logs, it doesn't just magically split in pieces like it does int the forest... beside this, all the animations are the same no matter which object you are using...even when you eat... I have to give a thumb down...and refund requested. There are better games for 14.99 euro. If you really want this game buy it on sale. Or just try it, if you are used to survival games you can figure out all in 1 hour... Maybe i will give it another chance when (and if) it will be out of beta.", "appid": "313120", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025632506", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1462190400.0}
