{"text": "At  the current state the game is, I dont recommend this game. Out of an hour of my gameplay half an hour was loading screen, the game crashed twice and a lot of in game functions dont even work like the map over lay. It has so so so much potential, reminds me of Sacred and Paath of Exile, can be an amazing game but the developers need to get their â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ together and make a game that paying customers deserve. The Graphics can be unstable, my specs are higher than needed and I still had to lower everything as it didnt work right and it kept glitching. Also the only map I got was the main map, very little space to see where to go anf how to come back to where I was. So much potential and I was so excited for the game, but until the bugs are fixed (especially freezing in the middle of the battle its infuriating) I cant recommend this. I will wait and see and keep playing to see if the game improves. I have high hopes, been dying for a new game like this for so long!", "appid": "424370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198200718251", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1537272000.0}
